                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>union among the Israelites of <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>, under<lb/> such\n                regulations as may be adopted by such<lb/> conference.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">The committee appointed by this Congn,<lb/> consists of\n                    <persName>Messrs A T Jones</persName>, <persName>Herman Van\n                Beil</persName>,<lb/> and the <persName>Revd Isaac Leeser</persName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Please inform the chairman of this<lb/> committee (<persName>Mr\n                    Jones</persName>) at an early date, what action<lb/> you may think proper to\n                take in this matter.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">J Solis Cohen</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Acting Secty</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">K K Beth El Emeth</p>"
                  },
